	   <div align="left" class="storytitle">San Diego Fanguard 2006 Write-Up: Part 2</div>
	   <div align="left" class="storyauth">By Nenjin Darkeyes</div>
	   <div align="left" class="storydetail">Feb  1, 2006, 16:10</div>
    
       </td>
       <td align=right valign=top>
      <div align="right" class="newslink"><a class="newslink" href="mailto:?subject=San%20Diego%20Fanguard%202006%20Write-Up%3A%20Part%202&body=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesafehouse.org%2Farticles%2Fevents%2Farticle_40.php">Email&nbsp;this&nbsp;article</a></div>
